	<SCENE>
		<ID>3</ID>
		<Title><![CDATA[Charlie arrives back in her hometown...]]></Title>
		<Desc><![CDATA[Charlie arrives back in her hometown, stopping at her brother's grave on the way home.]]></Desc>
