	<SCENE>
		<ID>20</ID>
		<Title><![CDATA[Lowell catches up with them at the cemetery and he and Charlie talk]]></Title>
		<Desc><![CDATA[Lowell catches up with them at the cemetery and he and Charlie talk]]></Desc>
